Dev & System Helpers
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Notes:
  note "idea"        append timestamped note to ~/notes.md
  note -l            show last 10 notes
  note               open ~/notes.md in neovim

Search:
  s pattern          search file contents (ripgrep, no color, line numbers)
  s pattern "*.py"   search only Python files

File transfer:
  serve              serve current directory over HTTP on port 8080
  serve 9090         use a different port
  (browse from laptop at http://<device-ip>:8080)

Backlight:
  bright             print current level (0-255)
  bright 150         set to a specific level
  bright +20         increase by 20
  bright -20         decrease by 20

Battery:
  battery            show charge level (human-readable)
  battery --tmux     compact format for tmux status bar

Hardware paths:
  /sys/firmware/picocalc/battery_percent
  i2c bus 1, addr 0x1f, reg 0x05 (backlight, write mask: reg | 0x80)
